{"hash":"7cb1e309567ed2fd7ca8b9a8eb220f1533e18a45","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"95d82bcf962b71caa6da2dbe0cf63701","title":"Introduction","description":"","path":"/docs/","timeToRead":1,"content":"<h1 id=\"introduction\"><a href=\"#introduction\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Introduction</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/SmartHub-Io/SmartHub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SmartHub</a> is a project for anyone who want to upgrade his home with some small digital helpers to improve his life.</p>\n<p><strong>This documantion and the project are still a WIP and we appreciate any help we can get :)</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"fast-by-default\"><a href=\"#fast-by-default\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Fast by default</h2>\n<p>This project is fast from the beginning and only has necessary stuff in it.\nIf you want more than the core offer you can extend it with plugins.</p>\n<h2 id=\"easy-for-everyone\"><a href=\"#easy-for-everyone\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Easy for everyone</h2>\n<p>We aim to write a software that is easy to understand and yet powerful to do all the things a user want it to do.\nFor the user we try to make it as intuitive and easy to use as possible.</p>\n<h4 id=\"thanks\"><a href=\"#thanks\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Thanks</h4>\n<p>This website is build by <a href=\"https://gridsome.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gridsome</a> a vue.js powered static site generator and is styled with this <a href=\"https://github.com/mrcrmn/docc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">theme</a>.\nThanks to the people behind these projects and thanks to everyone who wants to help us :)</p>\n","sidebar":"docs","next":"/docs/installation/","prev":"","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"Introduction","anchor":"#introduction"},{"depth":2,"value":"Fast by default","anchor":"#fast-by-default"},{"depth":2,"value":"Easy for everyone","anchor":"#easy-for-everyone"},{"depth":4,"value":"Thanks","anchor":"#thanks"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/docs/troubleshooting/","title":"Troubleshooting"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/smarthub-cli/","title":"SmartHub Cli"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/settings/","title":"Settings"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/prerequisites/","title":"Prerequisites"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/installation/","title":"Installation"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/","title":"Introduction"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/how-to-upgrade/","title":"How to Upgrade"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/how-to-create-a-plugin/","title":"How to create a Plugin"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/how-to-contribute/","title":"How to contribute"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/guide/","title":"Guide"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/faq/","title":"FAQ"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/endpoints/","title":"Server endpoints"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/devtools/","title":"Devtools"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/deploying/","title":"Deploying"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/concepts/","title":"Core Concepts"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/code-of-conduct/","title":"Code of Conduct"}},{"node":{"path":"/plugins/shelly/","title":"Shelly"}},{"node":{"path":"/plugins/mock/","title":"Mock"}},{"node":{"path":"/plugins/","title":"Introduction"}}]}},"context":{}}